{"books":[{"id":"jfjb","name":"解放军报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":12,"day":11}],"page_start":6,"page_end":6,"description":"","is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"title":"选代表","authors":[],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"幕启：一群小伙子在练习锣鼓，准备参加全乡的普选大会。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众男：瞧！姑娘们来了，让我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们来盘问盘问她们。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男甲：喂！姑娘们，去参加普"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选大会吗？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女甲：是啊！你们的锣鼓练习"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"得怎么样了？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女乙：今天的普选大会上，要"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看你们的锣鼓敲得响不响"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男乙：锣鼓敲得响不响，要看"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选的人合不合心，你们打"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"算选谁呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（唱）柱子要选檀香木，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表要选知心人；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她出身奴隶根子正，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去年参加了共产党。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）你们猜她是谁呢？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男：（唱）姑娘叫尼玛我们认"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"识，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"老人孩子都夸她，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今年刚刚二十五岁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年纪轻轻有啥本领？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（唱）有志不怕年纪轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛工作学习最积极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产劳动最辛勤，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"事事带头数第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男：（白）她的工作、学习、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动好，我们都看见了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但是啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）玻璃珠子外面亮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有件事儿我们最关心，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问她的思想红不红？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问她的骨头硬不硬？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（唱）翻身农奴有话找她"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"反动领主见她忙躲开，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说她思想红不红？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你说她骨头硬不硬？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男甲：（白）依我看，还是选"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎西好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众男：（白）对！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）扎西出身是贫农，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"年轻力壮思想红，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"生产学习劳动好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"斗争坏人他带头。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎西：（白）我不行啊！还是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"选尼玛好。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（白）是啊！尼玛就是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男：（白）你们说尼玛好，立"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"场坚定，有啥表现？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（唱）叛乱代理人搞复"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"辟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"她大胆揭露敢斗争，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"说道理来摆事实，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"难道你们没看见！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男： （唱）雄鹰勇不勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"暴风雪中才知道。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛对待坏人坏事，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"态度果断又勇敢。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）尼玛是透明的水"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"晶，表现好，思想也好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是啊！——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）扎西是闪光的珍"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办事公道又积极，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团支部里是委员，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"改良农具是第一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女： （唱）扎西生产搞得好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"扎西立场也坚定，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）可是呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）走社会主义的道"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"还是尼玛最坚定。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"男： （互相自语）是啊！在走"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社会主义道路上，还是尼"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"玛站得高，看得远。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）姑娘眼睛尖，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"珍珠看得清，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表选尼玛，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们同一心。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女：（唱）选举大事情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要把红旗插，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快去参加会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"快把锣鼓打。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"齐： （白）走啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女： （白）你们看，尼玛来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"了。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛：告诉你们一个好消息，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"咱们的庄稼今年又是好收"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"成。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众： 我们也告诉你一个好消"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"息。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女甲：我们正酝酿推选你当我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们的人民代表候选人哩！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛：这怎么行呢？我什么都"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不懂，怎么能当人民代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（唱）感谢众乡亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我尼玛选，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"办事我愿意，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只是没能力。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众： （唱）尼玛莫谦虚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"能力靠锻炼，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只要跟党走，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"群众就拥护。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛：（唱）代表责任重，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我怕担不起，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大家相信我，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我定加油学。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众： （唱）代表责任大，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"代表最光荣，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有党来撑腰，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尼玛莫害怕。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（白）尼玛不要客气，我"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"们是经过仔细讨论了的。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"女甲：快把鼓敲起来去参加大"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"众： 对，把鼓敲起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"表演者："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"团支部成员尼玛，多团支"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"部书记龙日等"}],"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}